#: apps/app/src/i18n/static-dom-seed.ts:615
#: apps/app/src/routes/legal-privacy-page.tsx:17
msgid "隐界会保存你的账号资料、聊天行为、动态内容和必要的运行日志，用于维持世界状态、消息同步和基础安全审计。"
msgstr "Yinjie stores your account profile, chat activity, posts, and necessary runtime logs to maintain world state, sync messages, and support basic safety audits."

#: apps/app/src/i18n/static-dom-seed.ts:616
#: apps/app/src/routes/legal-privacy-page.tsx:18
