msgstr "If you configure a dedicated API key in the app, the server stores it encrypted with current capabilities and never shows the full plaintext on the page."

#: apps/app/src/i18n/static-dom-seed.ts:617
#: apps/app/src/routes/legal-privacy-page.tsx:22
