msgstr "In remote mode, related data is sent to the world instance Core API and inference gateway. In self-hosted or specific deployments, it is stored in that instance's runtime directory and database."

#: apps/app/src/i18n/static-dom-seed.ts:619
#: apps/app/src/routes/legal-privacy-page.tsx:25
