#: apps/app/src/i18n/static-dom-seed.ts:624
#: apps/app/src/routes/legal-terms-page.tsx:17
msgid "你需要对自己发送的消息、评论、动态、资料修改和举报内容负责，不得利用隐界发布违法、骚扰、仇恨、侵权或误导性内容。"
msgstr "You are responsible for messages, comments, posts, profile edits, and reports you submit. Do not use Yinjie for illegal, harassing, hateful, infringing, or misleading content."

