#: apps/app/src/routes/legal-terms-page.tsx:18
msgid "如果你在世界里主动触发互动、加好友、创建群聊或调用 AI 能力，这些行为都会按产品能力进入对应的记录、通知和审计链路。"
msgstr "When you trigger interactions, add friends, create groups, or call AI capabilities in the world, those actions enter the related records, notifications, and audit flows."

